FastPattern.description: 1, TCPTrafficAudit: security,firewall - proto:tcp, action: Allow, Drop

FastPattern.pattern: ^\d+ [-\w.]+ +\d+ \d\d/\d\d/\d{4} \d\d:\d\d:\d\d \w+ \d : .+? \[\d\d\] Session: IPSEC\[[-\\\w.]+\]:\d+ physical addresses: remote [\d.]+ local [\d.]+
^\d+ [-\w.]+ +\d+ \d\d/\d\d/\d{4} \d\d:\d\d:\d\d \w+ \d : .+? \[\d\d\] Session: IPSEC\[[-\\\w.]+\]:\d+ assigned IP address [\d.]+, mask [\d.]+

FastPattern.matcher: ^(\d+) ([-\w.]+) +\d+ \d\d/\d\d/\d{4} \d\d:\d\d:\d\d \w+ \d : Session: (\w+)\[([^]]+)\]:(\d+) (Incoming client version \(.+?\), minimum version \(.+?\) push action \(.+?\).+)

FastPattern.description: 14, IPSecTrafficAudit: tIpsecDecap; Unable to send ESPUDP data

FastPattern.pattern: ^\d+ [-\w.]+ +\d+ \d\d/\d\d/\d{4} \d\d:\d\d:\d\d \w+ \d : .+? \[\d\d\] Session: PPTP\[[-\\\w.]+\]:\d+ physical addresses: remote [\d.]+ local [\d.]+
^\d+ [-\w.]+ +\d+ \d\d/\d\d/\d{4} \d\d:\d\d:\d\d \w+ \d : .+? \[\d\d\] Session: PPTP\[[-\\\w.]+\]:\d+ assigned IP address [\d.]+, mask [\d.]+

FastPattern.description: 29, EncryptedTrafficError: ssl; Checking chain: invalid cert
30, EncryptedTrafficError: ssl; Child cert not valid

Ospf_Global.State changed from \w+ to \w+ by user '(.+)'.*

38, PolicyModify: object changed from-to by user

^\d+ [-\w.]+ +\d+ \d\d/\d\d/\d{4} \d\d:\d\d:\d\d \w+ \d : routing \[\d\d\] VR .+: Starting .+ as (?:Master|Backup|master delayed Backup) for .+

51, ServiceInfo: radius auth; server rejected access

FastPattern.pattern: ^\d+ [-\w.]+ +\d+ \d\d/\d\d/\d{4} \d\d:\d\d:\d\d \w+ \d : Security \[\d\d\] Session: [^[]+\[.+\]:.+ session directed to use server .+
